data.description: Welcome To This One-story Brick Home Centrally Located To Schools, Shopping, And Just Minutes From Downtown Murray. The Interior Of The Home Features 3 Bedrooms, 2 Bathrooms, Spacious Kitchen, Living Area, Formal Dining Room, Large Utility Room, And An Added Sunroom (not Included In Sf Ft) With An Abundance Of Pella Windows. New Flooring Throughout The Majortiy Of Home. Outside You Will Find A Fenced-in Backyard, Storage Shed, Fire Pit, And A Detached Garage With Lots Of Storage. The Rear Of The Garage Has A Stairway Leading To A Large Bonus Room That Includes Electricity. Move In Ready!!
